726447f-a.folder: Cross Island Bouleva & 14th Road, Queens, NY
726447f-a.text:
Cross Island Boulevard, east side, between 14th Road and 15th Avenue(vantage point). Viewing northeast. along the Whitestone branch of the Long Island Railroad. The tracks can be seen passing under the 150th Place and Cross Island Boulevard bridges. View 2 is in the same direction from the latter bridge and
View 3 from the 14th Avenue Bridge.
P. L. Sperr  Narch 5, 1932
NO PEPRrDUCTIONS  Views 1-3
726447f-a.title: Queens: Cross Island Bouleva - 14th Road
